Print parameter space in the textual format accepted by irace.

Source: R/print_parameters.R
printParameters.Rd

Print parameter space in the textual format accepted by irace.

printParameters(params)

Arguments

params

(list()) Parameter object stored in irace.Rdata or read with irace::readParameters().

Examples

load(system.file(package="iraceplot", "exdata", "guide-example.Rdata", mustWork = TRUE))
printParameters(iraceResults$parameters)
#>   algorithm             "--" c (as,mmas,eas,ras,acs)
#> localsearch "--localsearch " c       (0,1,2,3)
#>       alpha       "--alpha " r           (0,5)
#>        beta        "--beta " r          (0,10)
#>         rho        "--rho  " r        (0.01,1)
#>        ants        "--ants " i         (5,100)
#>        nnls        "--nnls " i          (5,50) | localsearch %in% c(1, 2, 3)
#>          q0          "--q0 " r           (0,1) | algorithm %in% c("acs")
#>         dlb         "--dlb " c           (0,1) | localsearch %in% c(1, 2, 3)
#>     rasrank    "--rasranks " i         (1,100) | algorithm %in% c("ras")
#> elitistants "--elitistants " i         (1,750) | algorithm %in% c("eas")
